      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "From him, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Abdullah Bin Sinan, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The supplication is more piercing than the spear-heads of the iron’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "7. It is narrated from him (narrator of the Hadith above) from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from ‘Abd Allah ibn Sinan from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) has said, ‘Prayer, pleading before Allah for help, is more effective than spears of iron.’” "
        ]
      }
